{"id":168742,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/07/温州动车事故-微博投票集锦（图）/","date":"2011-07-26T02:32:46Z","modified":"2015-01-07T10:06:56Z","title":"温州动车事故 微博投票集锦（图）","content":"<p><strong>（1）大家对铁道部处理温州动车追尾事故处理的满意度调查</strong>（已于截图时间附近，北京时间26日凌晨被和谐）<br />\n<a href=\"http://vote.weibo.com/vid=691713\">http://vote.weibo.com/vid=691713</a></p>\n<p>截至截图时的参与人数：117,105</p>\n<p>基本满意 1,613 (1%)<br />\n非常满意 633 (1%)<br />\n呸！ 11,4851 (98%）</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-1.20.11-PM.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-168745\" title=\"Screen shot 2011-07-25 at 1.20.11 PM\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-1.20.11-PM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"571\" height=\"337\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-1.20.11-PM.png 714w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-1.20.11-PM-300x176.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 571px) 100vw, 571px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>（2）动车掩埋车体，你相信哪个理由？ </strong>（已于截图1个小时后，北京时间25日晚被和谐）<br />\n<a href=\"http://vote.weibo.com/vid=692952\">http://vote.weibo.com/vid=692952</a></p>\n<p>截至截图时的参与人数：62,926</p>\n<p>填池塘（昨天新闻报道）607 (1％)<br />\n更好地营救（早上QQ新闻弹出）506 (1％)<br />\n防止技术外泄（都市快报新闻） 429 (1％)<br />\n毁灭证据！！！！！！！！ 61,382 (98%)</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/动车掩埋车体.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-168743\" title=\"动车掩埋车体\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/动车掩埋车体.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"563\" height=\"505\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/动车掩埋车体.png 563w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/.png-300x269.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 563px) 100vw, 563px\" /></a><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/动车掩埋车体2.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-168744\" title=\"动车掩埋车体2\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/动车掩埋车体2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"565\" height=\"378\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/动车掩埋车体2.png 565w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/2-300x200.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 565px) 100vw, 565px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>（3）你对“温州动车追尾事故”的处理情况是否满意？</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://vote.weibo.com/vid=690625\">http://vote.weibo.com/vid=690625</a></p>\n<p>截至截图时的参与人数：89,647</p>\n<p>非常差劲，简直就是草菅人命。83,639 (93%)<br />\n不满意，应急措施差劲。 3,267 (4%)<br />\n还行，一般吧，还救出来了些人。948 (1％)</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.02.20-PM.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-168746\" title=\"Screen shot 2011-07-25 at 7.02.20 PM\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.02.20-PM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"575\" height=\"352\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.02.20-PM.png 575w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.02.20-PM-300x183.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>（4）温州动车脱轨，你觉得是天灾还是人祸？(2选1)</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://vote.weibo.com/vid=687270\">http://vote.weibo.com/vid=687270</a></p>\n<p>截至截图时的参与人数：49,560</p>\n<p>天灾 618 (1%)<br />\n人祸 48,942 (99%)</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.06.49-PM.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-168747\" title=\"Screen shot 2011-07-25 at 7.06.49 PM\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.06.49-PM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"564\" height=\"397\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.06.49-PM.png 564w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.06.49-PM-300x211.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 564px) 100vw, 564px\" /></a><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.06.59-PM.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-168748\" title=\"Screen shot 2011-07-25 at 7.06.59 PM\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.06.59-PM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"567\" height=\"327\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.06.59-PM.png 567w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.06.59-PM-300x173.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 567px) 100vw, 567px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>（5）大家相信动车遇难人数只有35人吗？</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://vote.weibo.com/vid=692608\">http://vote.weibo.com/vid=692608</a></p>\n<p>截至截图时的参与人数：29,303</p>\n<p>相信 643 (2%)<br />\n不相信 28,660 (98%)</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.10.23-PM.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-168750\" title=\"Screen shot 2011-07-25 at 7.10.23 PM\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.10.23-PM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"571\" height=\"292\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.10.23-PM.png 571w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.10.23-PM-300x153.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 571px) 100vw, 571px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>（6）你对中国红十会对温动车事故30万人道救助有何看法？</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://vote.weibo.com/vid=693097\">http://vote.weibo.com/vid=693097</a></p>\n<p>截至截图时的参与人数：7,612</p>\n<p>亲，留给郭美美买爱玛仕包吧！包邮哦，亲。6,942 (91%)<br />\n呸！怎么说也得给一辆玛莎拉蒂的钱呀！210 (3%)<br />\n此举一出，怕天下的小丑演员都要失业了。 156 (2%)<br />\n出手&#8221;阔绰&#8221;，被全国人民的唾沫星子砸死。304 (4%)</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.15.31-PM.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-168751\" title=\"Screen shot 2011-07-25 at 7.15.31 PM\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.15.31-PM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"568\" height=\"424\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.15.31-PM.png 568w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.15.31-PM-300x223.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 568px) 100vw, 568px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>（7）你觉得目前披露的动车相撞死亡35人的数字真实吗？</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://vote.weibo.com/vid=692936\">http://vote.weibo.com/vid=692936</a></p>\n<p>截至截图时的参与人数：4,746</p>\n<p>真实！事实如此！88 (2%)<br />\n我认为真实，上面说啥我信啥！110 (2%)<br />\n不真实，因为救援技术有限… 177 (4%)<br />\n不真实，因为组织只允许死35人… 4,371 (92%)</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.21.24-PM.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-168754\" title=\"Screen shot 2011-07-25 at 7.21.24 PM\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.21.24-PM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"577\" height=\"425\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.21.24-PM.png 577w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.21.24-PM-300x220.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 577px) 100vw, 577px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>（8）红十字会去温州募捐去了，看到募捐箱你怎么做？</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://vote.weibo.com/vid=693988\">http://vote.weibo.com/vid=693988</a></p>\n<p>截至截图时的参与人数：3,003</p>\n<p>要考虑很久，因为捐的钱有可能被拿去包二奶 220 (7%)<br />\n国家应该出钱赔偿，小小P民捐款起不到作用 193 (6%)<br />\n暗想：红十字会这趟是白跑了，浪费车票钱 41 (1%)<br />\n一分钱也不捐给红十字 141 (5%)<br />\n可以考虑给红十字募捐员工买饭盒，买瓶水 34 (1%)<br />\n拿板砖呼他丫的，还好意思出来募捐，不要脸 2,322 (77%)<br />\n理性的看待整件事，该捐款捐款 40 (1%)<br />\n寄望红十字，自己善心能帮助到需要帮助的人 12 (0%)</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.25.27-PM.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-168755\" title=\"Screen shot 2011-07-25 at 7.25.27 PM\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.25.27-PM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"568\" height=\"407\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.25.27-PM.png 568w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.25.27-PM-300x214.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 568px) 100vw, 568px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.25.36-PM.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-168756\" title=\"Screen shot 2011-07-25 at 7.25.36 PM\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.25.36-PM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"573\" height=\"463\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.25.36-PM.png 573w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.25.36-PM-300x242.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 573px) 100vw, 573px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>（9）“温州动车追尾”事故的处理情况令你满意吗？</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://vote.weibo.com/vid=695374\">http://vote.weibo.com/vid=695374</a></p>\n<p>截至截图时的参与人数：2,749</p>\n<p>非常满意，救援工作进行的很好 5 (0%)<br />\n满意，至少救出了一些人 7 (0%)<br />\n不满意，报道信息不全、救援工作开展的不好 52 (2%)<br />\n非常不满意，掩埋车体、“奇迹说”令人愤怒 2,685 (98%)</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.28.44-PM.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-168757\" title=\"Screen shot 2011-07-25 at 7.28.44 PM\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.28.44-PM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"558\" height=\"455\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.28.44-PM.png 558w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.28.44-PM-300x244.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 558px) 100vw, 558px\" /></a><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.30.27-PM.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-168759\" title=\"Screen shot 2011-07-25 at 7.30.27 PM\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.30.27-PM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"556\" height=\"352\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.30.27-PM.png 556w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.30.27-PM-300x189.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 556px) 100vw, 556px\" /></a><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-25-at-7.28.53-PM.png\"><br />\n</a></p>\n","author":1,"categories":[10466,13770,20534],"tags":[26638,8859,16285,17358]}